<!-- eslint-disable max-len -->
<!-- eslint-disable vue/no-multiple-template-root -->
<!-- eslint-disable vuejs-accessibility/label-has-for -->
<template>
    <label class="colors__label" :class="{done: color.done}" v-for="color in colors" :key="color.text">
        <input type="checkbox" v-model="color.done">
        {{ color.text }}
    </label>
</template>

<script>
export default ({
  data() {
    return {
      colors: [
        { text: 'White', done: true },
        { text: 'Black', done: false },
      ],
    };
  },
});
</script>
